author: David Gilbert, VICE News
title: China Is Now Blaming a Lone U.S. Cyclist For Coronavirus
description: China is pushing the unfounded conspiracy theory that the virus was created by the U.S. military and brought to China by an army athlete.
content:
A Chinese state-run newspaper is pushing an unfounded conspiracy theory that a U.S. military athlete was the patient zero of coronavirus.
